OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOutbreaks of
OL,6,Frain and drizzle clearing northern
OL,7,Fparts by midnight, although will
OL,8,Flinger across the south. Staying
OL,9,Fgenerally cloudy, with hill fog
OL,10,Fpatches across the Pennines. Winds
OL,11,Feasing, becoming generally light.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FCloudy but mostly dry in the
OL,14,Fnorth, however further outbreaks of
OL,15,Fmainly light rain are likely to linger
OL,16,Fin the south. Light winds. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
