OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fwith rain Saturday morning, gradually
OL,7,Fturning brighter, an overnight frost
OL,8,Fpossible. Winds strengthening Sunday
OL,9,Fand Monday, with some rain spreading
OL,10,Feast but also some drier spells. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
